
Benu
instance
Benu is a restaurant located in the SoMa district of downtown San Francisco opened in 2010 by Corey Lee. Formerly head chef at The French Laundry, Lee draws from many different cuisines, including Cantonese and Korean. In 2014, Benu was awarded the highest rating of three stars from the Michelin Guide. In 2015, Phaidon published Benu¨Ca collection of recipes and essays that explores the restaurant¡¯s food, influences, and people who make it possible¨Cwith forwards by Thomas Keller and David Chang, designed by Julia Hasting.